---
import MenuEN from '../../components/MenuEN.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Analytics from '../../components/Analytics.astro';
import '../../sass/general.scss';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto&family=Shrikhand&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Services and Prices at Bilene Kite Center, Mozambique</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Prices and services for Kitesurf and Wingsurf in Bilene, Mozambique">
    <meta name="keywords" content="prices, services, photo, photos, kite, kitesurf, kiteboard, wing, wingsurf, SUP, paddle, Mozambique, Bilene, lessons, lesson, coaching, progression, olk, one Launch kiteboarding">
    <Analytics />
</head>
<body>
    <MenuEN />

    <main>
        <section id="headsection">
            <img src="/images/5-prices/1.webp" alt="laptop on a desk">
            <h1 style="color:#d9dcdf;text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px black;">Services and Prices</h1>
            <h2 style="color:#d9dcdf;text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px black;">Mozambique at right price.</h2>
        </section>
        <section id="mainprice">
            <p>On this page, you will first find examples of typical packages, then the detailed prices of the services we offer in our kite center in Mozambique.
            </p>
            <h2>Examples of prices of full stay for 4 people <button class="toggle" data-target="#block1">...</button></h2>
            <div id="block1" class="block">
                <p>These prices are given for information only, as an example to give you an idea of the costs on site.
                They are offered in the form of packages, for groups of 4 people, the prices are given per person.
            </p>
            <p>
                Meals are not included in these prices, Bilene offers many restaurants and bars whose prices can vary enormously depending on their standings.
                Count on average between €5 and €10 per person for breakfasts, between €10 and €15 for lunches and dinners.
            </p>
            <section id="packages">
                <div class="packs">
                    <img src="/images/accueil/4.webp" alt="kitesurfer during a jump">
                    <aside>
                        <h2>Coaching</h2>
                        <p>8 days, 7 nights</p>
                    </aside>
                    <p>included:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Airport Transfers</li>
                        <li>Accommodation in a 2-bedroom bungalow (2p per room)</li>
                        <li>OLK coaching week</li>
                        <li>5h SUP rental</li>
                        <li>1 Speed Spot trip</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="price">
                        <div>
                            <p>From:</p>
                            <p>590 €</p>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/en/information-mozambique#contactus"><button>Contact us</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="packs">
                    <img src="/images/3-school/9.webp" alt="kitesurfer on the water">
                    <aside>
                        <h2>Passionate Riders</h2>
                        <p>8 days, 7 nights</p>
                    </aside>
                    <p>included:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Airport Transfers</li>
                        <li>Accommodation in a 2-bedroom bungalow (2p per room)</li>
                        <li>Storage</li>
                        <li>5h SUP rental</li>
                        <li>1 Speed Spot trip</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="price">
                        <div>
                            <p>From:</p>
                            <p>360 €</p>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/en/information-mozambique#contactus"><button>Contact us</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="packs">
                    <img src="/images/accueil/3.webp" alt="kitesurf students and instructor">
                    <aside>
                        <h2>Easy Spot Beginners</h2>
                        <p>8 days, 7 nights</p>
                    </aside>
                    <p>included:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Airport Transfers</li>
                        <li>Accommodation in a 2-bedroom bungalow (2p per room)</li>
                        <li>10 hours kitesurf lesson</li>
                        <li>5h SUP rental</li>
                        <li>1 Speed Spot trip</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="price">
                        <div>
                            <p>From:</p>
                            <p>559 €</p>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/en/information-mozambique#contactus"><button>Contact us</button></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="prixtrips">
            <h2>Kitesurfing Trips in Mozambique</h2>
            <p>We offer complete trips to the best spots on the southern coast of Mozambique. You can discover them on our dedicated page.
                Prices vary according to many parameters, we suggest you make an estimate.
                To give a basic idea, indicative only, for a group of 4 people, the average is around 100€/day/person, including accommodation, transport,
                guiding on the spots, beach boy, and 2 meals per day.
            </p>
            <div class="vimeo" style="padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;">
                <iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/342077640?h=04157a2824&portrait=0" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="prixlessons">
            <h2>Kite Center Prices</h2>
            <p>
                Here is the list of prices charged at the kite center. We are located directly on the beach of the spot, in an authentic hotel complex pleasantly integrated into nature: the Palmeiras complex. It offers several types of accommodation,
                wifi, shop, as well as a restaurant and beach bar directly on <a href="/en/the-kitesurf-spot-in-bilene-mozambique">the spot</a>.
            </p>
            <div class="groupPrice">
                <img src="/images/5-prices/11.webp" alt="price list" loading="lazy">
                <img src="/images/5-prices/12.webp" alt="price list" loading="lazy">
            </div>
            <div class="groupPrice">
                <img src="/images/5-prices/13.webp" alt="price list" loading="lazy">
                <img src="/images/5-prices/14.webp" alt="price list" loading="lazy">
            </div>
            <div class="groupPrice">
                <img src="/images/5-prices/15.webp" alt="price list" loading="lazy">
                <img src="/images/5-prices/16.webp" alt="price list" loading="lazy">
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
    <script is:inline src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script>
</body>
</html>